<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Support Request for Tour Booking</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .header h2 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #007BFF;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .content p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .content p strong {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 150px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            color: #777;
        }

        .footer b {
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            border-bottom: 1px double #000;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Customer Support Request for Booking</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Full Name:</strong> {{fullName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{phone}}</p>
            <p><strong>Other Request:</strong> {{otherRequest}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
            <b style="text-transform: uppercase;">Global Travel Viet</b>
            <p>Hotline: 003343682463</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:demo@gmail.com">demo@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p>Website: <a href="http://www.abc.com">www.abc.com</a></p>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>